244
00:18:59,277 --> 00:19:01,238
Awak sediakan makanan ritual?

245
00:19:01,321 --> 00:19:02,739
Nenek yang buatkan.

246
00:19:02,822 --> 00:19:04,157
Tapi nenek penganut Katolik.

247
00:19:04,783 --> 00:19:06,076
Dia berfikiran terbuka.

248
00:19:09,079 --> 00:19:10,288
Cik Won, Cik Seo.

249
00:19:16,294 --> 00:19:20,048
KERETA PANDU SENDIRI MORNING AI, MOMO
TERIMA LESEN PENGGUNAAN SEMENTARA

250
00:19:21,716 --> 00:19:23,969
Kenapa Shin Hyeon dan Shin Jeong
ada di situ?

251
00:19:27,681 --> 00:19:29,015
Tak mungkin.

252
00:19:31,309 --> 00:19:32,227
Apa?

253
