Terima kasih.

254
00:19:34,854 --> 00:19:37,232
Baru balik makan tengah hari?
Awak makan di mana?

255
00:19:37,315 --> 00:19:39,317
Kami perlu laporkan kami makan di mana?

256
00:19:39,401 --> 00:19:41,486
Tak. Saya rasa saya nampak awak tadi.

257
00:19:41,570 --> 00:19:43,446
Kami makan di Kafeteria Sand Box.

258
00:19:46,533 --> 00:19:49,828
Betullah mereka jumpa
